{
  "texts": [
    "In order to improve the recognition accuracy of the Sichuan dialect, they constructed a Sichuan dialect pronunciation dictionary.",
    "However, DNN based approaches often require large amounts of data and substantial computational power for training, which is a drawback compared to traditional approaches.",
    "Another issue in training Chinese DSR models is the need to force the alignment of dialect sequences to generate reference state labels for each frame.",
    "Convolutional neural network (CNN) is one of the deep neural-network architectures.",
    "It can effectively process time series data and performs well in speech recognition."
  ]
}